rows.label: tlk00030105_msg0001
rows.name:
Well, well, well! Me pleased to see you
have returned. Unharmed, no less!

rows.label: tlk00030105_msg0002
rows.name:
Me thought you sunk along with ancient
vessel, but this very pleasant surprise!

rows.label: tlk00030105_msg0003
rows.name:
Rex, you have earned Bahn's favor.
Would be most propitious to have
you continue line of work!

rows.label: tlk00030105_msg0101
rows.name:
Oh, busy busy Bahn... Bahn's plans
gone a little bit awry... Back to Bahn's
drawing board!
